NAME
     xprotectd – XProtect Daemon

SYNOPSIS
     xprotectd [-v]

DESCRIPTION
     xprotectd is a subsystem of XProtect, a component of MacOS which
     automatically detects and blocks the execution of known malware.

FILES
     /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.security.xprotectd.plist  The
                                                                       launchd.plist(5)
                                                                       for
                                                                       xprotectd.

